No. 1023,

October Term, 1940.

Pickett, General Chairman, v. Union Terminal Co.; Williams et al. v. Jacksonville Terminal Co.; and D’Oench, Duhme & Co., Inc. v. Federal Deposit Insurance Corp. No. 112. No. 206. March 30, 1942.

Petitions for rehearing denied.

Mr. Justice Roberts took no part in the consideration or decision of these applications.
